    • Method Detail

      • changeSprites

        public void changeSprites()
        This method changes the sprite of the object. It is called after the player character interacts with the objects, and it sets the solid boolean value to false if it used to be true (which means that now the player character can pass through it) and it changes the interacted boolean value to true after interaction
        Parameters:
        null -
